{"tid":1608121,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"【國殤向記者派食物包】 食唔撚死要感謝黨","createTime":"2019-10-01T07:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T19:38:10.000Z","uid":175314,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86cc849cc13fd227e84484eb35c8cbafc88101a2","tid":1608121,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3swGCMW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3swGCMW.jpg&h=2f2503c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uepXVyC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuepXVyC.jpg&h=8181fba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京今早舉行中共建政70周年大閱兵及群眾巡遊，保安異常嚴密，進入封鎖區內的記者及觀眾約有3萬人，需經過2次安檢。凌晨2時，已有記者到場採訪，但封鎖區內無食肆或商店提供飲食，如何解決肚餓問題呢？大會就特別派發一袋食物包給記者，以便他們能夠撐足成朝。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">這個食物包以透明膠袋包裝，並加以密封，裏面有數片方包、2支礦泉水、元氣棒（麵包）、1盒酸梅汁、2包朱克力餅、2包濕紙巾、1包普通紙巾、1包肉圓、1條香腸、1包酸菜和數粒糖。</span>全部都是內地市場購買得的廉價食物，並非特別為這次建政70周年而生產或包裝的，看上去似乎不太吸引，但要支撐一個早上應該不成問題。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成袋垃圾咁真係你食埋我份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過香港啲狗警可能爭住食要感謝黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉自《蘋果日報》"},{"pid":"00f6def56ac00745951d3ea9a6c67bdaa2eb65c4","tid":1608121,"uid":279253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:55:26.000Z","msg":"食完都怕折壽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4503d8fc19904d02b9c03f575b1c1e233f4e975f","tid":1608121,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00f6def56ac00745951d3ea9a6c67bdaa2eb65c4","tid":1608121,"uid":279253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:55:26.000Z","msg":"食完都怕折壽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"係中共減少人口老化嘅政策嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa88eff957dd7459a1fa39ef98d5c7601b0e7aae","tid":1608121,"uid":3873,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:56:36.000Z","msg":"嗰兩包濕紙巾, 就咁睇我以為係杜蕾斯黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f17045fcf7e944db1311230dda171c3590d7aaa","tid":1608121,"uid":283071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:38:10.000Z","msg":"數片方包、元氣棒（麵包）<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}